<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<data>
	<father type="crossbow">
		<bullet color="yagold" kind="particle" composeLv="99" dropLevelArr="999">
			<name>consArcher</name><dpsMul>2.5</dpsMul><uiDpsMul>7.7</uiDpsMul>
			<cnName>射手座</cnName><iconUrl>newGun/consArcherIcon</iconUrl>
			<attackType>holy</attackType><noMagneticB>1</noMagneticB>
			<aiShootRange>600</aiShootRange><!-- ai射程 -->
			<!--基本-->
			<capacity>50</capacity>
			<attackGap>1.6</attackGap>
			<attackDelay>1.6</attackDelay>
			<crossbowD focoB="1" minDelayMul="0.4" vAtt="1" />
			<reloadGap>1.5</reloadGap>
			<bulletWidth>40</bulletWidth>
			<!--武器属性------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<armsArmMul>0.65</armsArmMul>
			<upValue>10</upValue>
			<shootShakeAngle>30</shootShakeAngle>
			<shootRecoil>7</shootRecoil>
			<screenShakeValue>8</screenShakeValue>
			<!--基本属性------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<noShakeTime>0.5</noShakeTime>
			<bulletLife>16</bulletLife>
			<hitType>rect</hitType>
			<!--运动属性------------------------------------------------------------ -->	
			<bulletSpeed>10</bulletSpeed>
			<speedD />
			<followD value="0.25" delay="7" shootCY="-2000" noLM="1" />
			<!--特殊------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<gravity>0.08</gravity>
			<penetrationGap>1000</penetrationGap>
			<skillArr>Hit_Spurting_ArmsSkill</skillArr>
			<godSkillArr>oldSugarArcher,fullCrushGod</godSkillArr>
			<boomD bodyB="1" radius="150" />
			<!--图像动画属性------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<flipX>1</flipX>
			<bulletImgUrl name="consArcherBullet"></bulletImgUrl>
			<smokeImgUrl name="smallMissleSmokeSm"></smokeImgUrl>
			<hitImgUrl name="yearDog_boom"></hitImgUrl>
			<fireImgUrl name="enegryGunFire"></fireImgUrl>
			<shootSoundUrl>specialGun/skyArchSound</shootSoundUrl>
			<!--图像范围------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<bodyImgRange>newGun/consArcher</bodyImgRange>
			<bulletImgRange>specialGun/bullet</bulletImgRange>
			<info>子弹如流星划出优雅抛物线，滞空越久，聚集的能量越高。当坠落的星光最终触及目标，积蓄的星芒之力将对敌人造成毁灭性打击。</info>
			<description></description>
		</bullet>
	</father>
	<father name="godArmsSkill" cnName="神级武器技能">
		<skill name="星芒之力">
			<name>oldSugarArcher</name>
			<cnName>星芒之力</cnName><noRandomListB>1</noRandomListB><ignoreImmunityB>1</ignoreImmunityB><noSkillDodgeB>1</noSkillDodgeB>
			<!--触发条件与目标------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<conditionType>passive</conditionType><changeHurtB>1</changeHurtB>
			<condition>hit</condition>
			<target>target</target>
			<!--效果------------------------------------------------------------ -->
			<addType>instant</addType>
			<effectType>oldSugar</effectType>
			<mul>5</mul>
			<secMul>75</secMul>
			<description>借助星芒之力对敌人造成毁灭性打击！子弹每存在1秒，就增加[mul]的伤害，最高增加[secMul]的伤害。8秒后子弹开始对敌人进行弱跟踪。</description>
		</skill>
	</father>
</data>